detailedDescription:
Please, mark it as "black triangle sighting", not like ufo sighting.

two black monoliths 3-4 meters high advancing slowly and vertically  in line
========================================================================

yesterday, holy thursday, i decided to approach to a rural road 20 km from seville, near gerena, where i used to fly model airplanes a while ago. as there was a tractor picking up water from the stream that blocked my way, i went to a road that lies ahead. i decided to take a walk, i took my chair-cane and walked 1600 meters and i stopped to smoke a cigarette under a mass of reeds.

the day was very peaceful, a little wind blew, and the sky was clear. it was 8:15 p.M. and i would have been sitting for 10 minutes when i saw in front of me, in the distance,  little less than 500 meters, two "black monoliths" separated 50 meters apart, that were going on the road in a south-north direction . they went slowly, at ground level, vertically,  as if levitating, i was amazed because although they were located 470 meters from me (i consulted later in google earth) i estimated their height in 3-4 meters.

i repeat, they went slowly, about 50 km / h, which is impossible with a car on that dirt road destroyed because the tracks of the tractors after the recent rains had left a huge furrows. however, both monoliths moved uniformly, without rectifying the direction or slowing down. honestly, they must have been levitating on the road or something similar, although the proximity of a wheat field prevented me from seeing it clearly.
they moved on edge, presenting the largest plane in my direction, they were of a satin black tone, that is, slightly bright. its form was a perfect parallelepiped, which reminded me a lot of the monolith of the famous movie "2001 an space odyssey". it is not coincidence that the famous nasa astronomer carl sagan was the one who advised stanley kubrik to include the famous monolith as a result of some strange observations made from the lunar orbit by the apollo x astronauts in 1969.

what the hell is that? i thought at first. i did not know how to identify them, i was amazed, with my eyes wide opened and wishing they would pass by as soon as possible and they didnt  change their direction towards me. which they did not do, fortunately, although now i regret it. even so it took about 30 seconds to do 430 meters, which indicates a speed of 51 km / h. . i must admit that a great fear assaulted me, but even so i followed them closely until they vanished suddenly when reaching the top of the hill, only 3 meters of depression from the top to the bottom.


========================================================

dos monolitos negros de 3-4 metros de altura avanzando lenta y verticalmente en linea


ayer, jueves santo, decidí acercarme a un camino rural  a 20 kms de sevilla, cerca de gerena, donde yo volaba aviones de aeromodelismo hace un tiempo. como había un tractor cogiendo agua del riachuelo que me bloqueaba  el paso, me fui a un camino que hay mas adelante. decidí dar un paseo, cogí mi silla-baston y ande 1600 metros y me paré para fumar un cigarrillo debajo de un macizo de cañas. 
el día era muy apacible, soplaba un poco de viento, y el cielo estaba despejado. eran las 20:15 horas y llevaría 10 minutos sentado cuando vi frente a mi, en la distancia, a poco menos de 500   metros, dos "monolitos negros" separados unos 50 metros entre si, que iban por el camino en sentido sur-norte.  iban despacio, por el suelo, verticalmente, como levitando, me quedé asombrado porque  aunque  estaban situados a 470 metros de mi (lo consulté después en google earth) estimé su altura en 3-4 metros.
 repito, iban despacio, a unos 50 km/h, lo cual es imposible con un coche por ese camino de tierra destrozado porque las rodadas de los tractores tras las recientes lluvias habían dejado unos surcos enormes.  sin embargo, ambos monolitos se desplazaban de manera uniforme, sin rectificar la dirección ni aminorar la velocidad. sinceramente, debían estar levitando sobre el camino o algo parecido, aunque la proximidad de un campo de trigo me impidió verlo claramente. 
se desplazaban de canto, presentando el plano mayor en mi dirección, eran de un tono negro satinado, es decir, ligeramente brillantes. su forma era de un paralelepípedo perfecto, cosa que recordaba mucho al monolito de la famosa película "2001 una odisea en el espacio". no es casualidad que el famoso astrónomo de la nasa carl sagan fuera quien aconsejó a stanley kubrik incluir el famoso monolito a raíz de unas extrañas observaciones realizadas desde la órbita lunar por los astronautas del apolo x en 1969.

¿qué demonios es eso?, pensé en un primer momento. no supe identificarlos, me quedé estupefacto, con los ojos abiertos como platos y deseando que pasarán de largo lo antes posible y no cambiaran de dirección hacia mi. cosa que no hicieron, afortunadamente, aunque ahora lo lamento. aún así tardaron unos 30 segundos en hacer 430 metros, lo que arroja una velocidad de 51 km/h. . he de reconocer que me asaltó un gran temor, pero aún así los segui atentamente hasta que se desvanecieron subitamente al alcanzar  la cima de la vaguada, de tan solo 3 metros de depresión.
description: Two 3-4 meters black monoliths  advancing slowly and vertically  in line

detailedDescription:
close encounter of the third kind with an humanoid/entity human-like
encuentro cercano en la tercera fase con un humanoide/entidad como-humano

quiero informar de un fortuito caso de avistamiento ovni/humanoide/tercera fase acaecido en una dehesa próxima a sevilla el 5 de abril de 2017. ¡ y que duró 24 horas !

esto sucedio en un lugar muy próximo a sevilla. es tan extraño el incidente que todo este asunto se hace increíble y difícil de creer incluso para personas especializadas en la fenomenología ovni. pienso que este incidente se sale de la escala de lo creíble, pero realmente sucedió y yo lo vi tal y como lo escribo. es un "encuentro cercano" tan fantástico que por fuerza es verdad. ni hollywood podría imaginar una historia así. 

existen pruebas grabadas de camaras de seguridad e incluso testigos parciales del hecho. en cualquier caso no puedo acceder a dichas grabaciones sin implicarme. 

vayamos al caso. estaba yo en un campo muy próximo a sevilla capital viendo gente volando aviones de aeromodelismo.  para ver mejor un aeromodelo que me interesó saqué mis prismáticos del coche.  cuando aterrizó el aeromodelo me fijé que al fondo del campo había un coche parado en un sitio donde nunca jamás se pone nadie. ! qué raro, pensé¡  y lo observé detenidamente. en un primer momento fué a través de una fortuita observación con prismaticos de un sujeto (un simple deportista, pensé yo) situado a 650 metros de mí, que lanzaba una pertiga de 2,50 mts y 5 cm de diametro a 350 metros sin esfuerzo, sin parábola, sin carrera, como si lanzara un pequeño dardo. yo creo que la pértiga apantallaba la gravedad con algún tipo de recubrimiento o pintura antigravitatoria ya que era completamente lisa y no emitía ningún sonido. ese día era un perfecto día de primavera, cielo despejado, sol radiante y ligera brisa del norte. era media tarde y al ser un terreno completamente llano, sin árboles ni arbustos, la visibilidad era perfecta.

este sujeto al que llamaré ultra-humano seguía una rutina invariable. cuando recogía la pértiga volvía junto al coche tranquilamente, sin temor, la llevaba en posición vertical, sin ocultarla. se quedaba parado junto al coche, con la pértiga en posición horizontal un par de minutos y de repente y sin ningún esfuerzo y sin tomar carrera la lanzaba siempre en la misma dirección. hacia el oeste. inmediatamente comenzaba a andar para recuperarla, tranquilamente, como dando un paseo. y así una y otra vez durante la hora que estuve observándole.

es dificil explicarlo, pero no cambié el chip a modo "realidad mágica" sino que pensé que esa sobrehumana capacidad era explicable. como la ignorancia es atrevida y el lugar es muy familiar para mi, quise acercarme a él para preguntarle. el caso es que me vió y se aproximó a mi ¡ siendo invisible! lo sé porque yo iba mirando hacia delante y toda la zona de lanzamiento quedaba dentro de mi campo visual, pudiendo yo ver todo lo que acontecía a más de un kilómetro frente a mi, excepto a este ultra-humano que se "materializo" amenazante frente a mí, con brazos en jarra y piernas abiertas,(no llevaba la pértiga con él) .

se paró a 50 metros o menos frente a mi, , mirándome fijamente sin moverse y yo me quedé petrificado mirándole tambien durante unos 5 segundos, provocandome instantáneamente como un colapso mental, la palabra exacta sería "estado de grogui" de total confusión que me hizo retroceder, dar dos vueltas amplias de unos 10 metros en torno a mí y olvidarme literalmente de todo lo que había sucedido. lo recuerdo ahora porque producido el "encontronazo" regrese tranquilamente a mi coche (situado a 500 metros de distancia) sin volver la vista atras y sin ningún temor ¡porque ya no recordaba nada! esta pérdida de memoria me duró tres días, si no hubiera ido al día siguiente para comprobar si seguía allí o si había dejado algun resto o señal en la zona cero. fuí al cabo de 3 días y no encontré nada, ni huellas, ni restos, ni señales.... nada de nada. y algo muy importante, el "visitante" ya no ha vuelto más, y creo que ya no lo volveré a ver nunca jamás.

después de 9 meses y más de 160 veces me he acercado al lugar un busca de alguna prueba, pero sin resultado. la sorpresa vino el pasado 16 de noviembre en un documental sobre los geoglifos en el cual apareció el sujeto humanoide que había visto. se encuentra en inglaterra y se llama "el hombre largo de wilmington"  (long man of wilmington) figura de culto desde hace siglos y de origen desconocido. ¿cómo puede ser que un ser así no haya sido visto por alguién más en 4 siglos? es cierto que su actividad era muy discreta y que se confundía con un deportista, pero aún así su indumentaria era extraña. espero que algún lector/investigador consiga las fotos satelite de ese día y esa zona, porque él estuvo allí durante 24 horas. hasta que llegue ese día sólo puedo informar con mis testimonios y mis dibujos descriptivos.

========================================

actualización al día 5 de marzo de 2018 (11 meses después del incidente)
llevo 1 mes soñando todas las noches el incidente, reviviéndolo tal y como ocurrió. se ha convertido en una pesadilla recurrente todas las noches. ¿cómo pudo afectarme así si sólo el contacto visual me pareció que duro unos 5 segundos? espero que llegue el próximo dia 5 de abril.
description: Close encounter of the third kind with an humanoid/entity  human-like

detailedDescription:
Answers:

1. i was in a landing track for seeing plane models flying.

4. about the fellow: athletic man, naked torso, tight long trousers, black boots, throwing a large pole out of human capabilities (1150 feet), no parabole, no taking a career, efortless like throwing a small dart. repetitive movements, all day. i believe  that pole/pertiga created a passive antigravity shield without visible external devices, as if it were a coating or a painting.
note: his appearance is identical to the "long man from wilmington" (england), an ancient hill figure

about the car: black color, tinted windows, stopped near the man, closed doors, high-end car, very important: without license plate. parked in an unusual place. the man didnt visit the car.

5.I surprised myself at the first moment. i looked at him, i could see him about an hour, doing the same routine. throwing, walking, and picking up his  pole. i thought of that large distance was totally explainable. so i walked towards him, but he approached i dont know how, but he materialized in front of me (i did not see the moment) and he caused me a mental conmotion like a grogi state. then i backed up, i circled twice around me and returned to my car. i lost my memory of all this for three days, then i remembered it.

detailedDescription:
On 27th october 2017 driving southward from huercal overa to turre on the a7/e15 at aprox 11-11.30 am at 50mph i noticed a white arrow shaped whispy cloud suddenly appear in a clear clear blue sky at approx 45 degrees to my position. distance from me impossible to tell. the cloud stated to disperse westward and revealed a round shining ball the size of an asprin. as i watched the cloud disappeared as fast  as it had appeared and the shining ball which seemed stationary for a brief moment just got smaller until it was out of sight altogether.
as i was on the motorway with fast moving traffic i was unable to stop , take photos or more accurate compass readings. it was nothing on my windsheild as the car had been in the car wash 1 hour earlier.
i felt quite elated as this was my third ufo sighting, my first being in papua new guinea wher i had to fill in enough forms in triplicate and suffer  stupid remarks from an australian agent i vowed not to report any further sightings, and my second sighting which was in spain and was later reported in the local newspaper by over 200 persons.
description: Observed  in clear blue sky from car while travelling on a7 just passed vera turnoff

detailedDescription:
On september 3rd 2014 at around 9 15 pm, (after dark), while having dinner with my family, on vacation at the alvor praia hotel, alvor, in portugal's argarve district. my son (then 31 years old) and i saw a red-orange ball rise out of the sea, about 500 yards off tres irmaos beach in front of the hotel. we were looking down from the hotel's open air dining terrace (about 100 ft above sea level) towards the west when we saw the very bright object come up vertically out of the sea (lagos bay). we could see it rise vertically in the sky against the back-drop of the town lights of lagos, across the bay. to the west. the object climbed slowly to a height of i estimate a thousand feet (at least). the object then executed a curved flight in a parabola to the horizontal. it then immediately 'took off' to the west, along the coastline at 'jaw dropping speed' i timed the object and estimated it's recessional speed at about 1 mile per second! no sound! no sonic boom. 

the following morning, a portuguese navy ship was present in the bay! this ship  looked to be a hydrographic survey ship, from comparisons that we did 'real-time' on the internet, while looking at the ship with binoculars.  there was also a helicopter overhead and what looked to be men ain  rubber boat, from the navy ship, taking samples in the sea. my family have vacationed at this same spot for 10 years and have never seen a portuguese navy ship in the bay. 

this event made a very deep, lasting impression on my son and i. 

the sky in the area was clear at the time, with starlight and viewing conditions were excellent. i regularly watch aircraft flying to and from faro airport nearby at this location. the speed of this orange ball was just incredible. it tooth breath away! i estimate the size of this spherical object around 30 ft minimum. diameter perhaps double that size. the light was pinkish-orange-red. never seen a color like it. it looked to me to be a ball of plasma. however the outline of the light was very sharp. as it receded it pulsated very slightly. 

what was it??? absolutely no idea.

hundreds of holidaymakers in that busy vacation area and town (avor and lagos) must have seen this event. hence the presence next day of a portuguese navy vessel in he bay.
flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change
description: Red spherical ball or sphere emitting red-orange-pink light similar in quality to a neon street light emerged from sea in lagos bay portugal, hovered and took off at incredible speed. l

detailedDescription:

(sorry for my english)

detailedDescription:
Incident happened on 8th day of our spain trip (seville). we stayed at q&q suite cathedral duplex apartment from 4-6 august 2017. around 12:30 midnight on 5th august, we have drink at the rooftop facing the cathedral de seville. at about 12:15am i saw a grey-silver object (looks like a cloud changing shape) moving from nw direction with a black-shadow object above the grey-silver cloud/beam - no sound.  at first i though it was a silver balloon because i was too focus on the grey-silver cloud/beam. 

the tricky part was my husband and my son saw the black-oval-like object (swinging) with 8 lights underneath but i can only see the "cloud/beam" with dark shadow above (no lights).  if i put all the testimonial together, the "cloud/beam" is moving parallel with the black-oval-like object.  

before the sighting of object, i was shouting to the sky and complaining why i can't see the stars nor ufo even travel from another part of world to europe.  when i was waiting for my husband/son to join for a drink at the rooftop, i saw the cloud/beam object flew towards our direction.  later then my husband and son saw the black-oval-like ufo flew over our apartment.
description: Black color swing w/ 8 light bottom and mid-grey cloud/beam parallel moving object

detailedDescription:
Because the temperatures in spain have been so hot, we have taken to sitting out on the roof terrace in the late evening to enjoy the coolness and look at the night sky.
 
on monday we were looking out at the bright full moon which was in the southern aspect of the sky. the lower horizon was fairly misty in the valleys coming up from the coast, so the moon was beautiful. because it was so bright, i was curious as to how many stars we would see.
looking up towards the ne, my eye caught a bright flash of what could have been a star just uncovered by a cloud, then covered again - however, there was not a cloud in the sky.

curiosity made me keep looking in the area of the sky to try to figure out if it was a plane and its trajectory.
i know it was not a sattelite as we had observed one a few days previously as a single light travelling in a straight line across the sky from sse to nnw with no trail.
nor was it a shooting star, which we see regularly.
i pointed it out to my husband who confirmed that he too saw it and its eratic placement in the sky.

the second flash was about 8 seconds later heading towards the east.
the next one was back towards the north.
i sat down in order to 'frame' the area i was watching, using the posts and poles of the of the terrace, to have a reference in case i was wobbling.
the next few flashes i noted the direction changes were random, as if it were spiraling or looping the loop.
the time interval between flashes varied between 3 and 12 seconds appart.
as i was watching, and anticipating where the next one would be, i noted that associated with the flash was a pinpoint of light that i could follow with the naked eye. the bright flash seemed to eminate from this point every time.
after a final swirl of movement that i was able to clearly see, it flashed really bright and then the brighter dot streaked off leaving a faint trail, in a nw direction and was gone.

i felt intrigued and convinced that it was a ufo.

one thought i had was that if it was a craft with one surface that was more reflective than the others, then as it turned in flight, it may have flashed with the reflection of the bright moon that was in the nearly opposite quadrant of the sky. that would explain why i felt it was spiraling - almost 'playing'.

there are large eagles that soar during the day in the jimena area as the village is situated at the base of a castle that had value as a strategic point at the time of the moors and the romans. the apparent spiraling movements of the lights reminded me of their soaring flight with the air currents, and how they can disappear from view when end-on.

i have spoken about this to colleagues at work and was told that there are others who have witnessed exactly the same phenomenon in the same region, but viewing from further west - looking east and north over the national park.

please note, there is a supposed 'top secret' us base at 36.479370, -5.599288 - see file 2
flightPath: Straight-line path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering
description: Bright flash of light that changed course and appeared to spiral bepore streaking off

detailedDescription: Me and a friend were sitting on the roof of our apartment listening to music and i looked up, seeing 10 objects moving at uniform speed across the sky, 3/4 of which were changing direction in circle/ spiral patterns. they moved what i believe to be in a southerly direction, and we're followed by 3 ufos moving in a v shape with another 2 behind them 5 minutes later. orbs were also seen in the location moving in the same direction as the other ufos. none of them made a noise, and were not aircraft you would usually identify in the sky. we were near an airport so we know the distance and noise of these craft and these were definitely not one of them. once i saw it i leapt up out of my chair and for the following hot i felt so happy and excited to see them but also a little ut scared. as soon as i saw it i was overcome with lots of emotion that never show together. i was frightened, happy, sad, delighted all at once. we lost sight of the object as they moved out of eyesight
description: 10 lights overhead changing direction with no noise followed by 5 more 5 minutes later

detailedDescription: Yesterday (15th of june) at about 12:40 am in the night i looked outside my window to the sea and saw the light blinking every 2 seconds. at first i though it was an airplane, so i went to open an app called "flightradar24" to track planes. there was no planes above this area. alright, i though, i grabbed my binoculars and looked at the lights. i was shocked, when i saw actually not 1 but 3 of them through binoculars  forming a triangle. one of them was yellow, the other two were reddish or greenish color. and they kept moving to the left and then back to the right. sometimes just sitting in the sky at one spot about a minute. they were flying about 20 minutes or so, before disappearing.
description: At around 12:40 am i saw three lights changing path and direction, forming triangle above the sea.

detailedDescription:
I was driving my car in the late afternoon because i was going to the university in portimão. i was in my car when i visualized a yellow ball that radiated in all directions so bright, left no trace, and had a steady speed in the way it did, i stared at this ball in the sky to try to observe the details of it but realized that it was not an airplane or any meteorological object because it had no engines or wings nor did it leave a trail, it came to an altitude sufficient to cross the sky and to pass over two hills that are in the right side next to via do infante in the access node of faro but as they are tall the bright yellow ball when passing over them i left it to see it because it went north and i was driving my car and i went west towards portimão.
the sky that afternoon was clean and very blue what caught my attention was to observe this ball of bright yellow light following at the same speed and in the same way approaching more and more of the place that i was on the road until slowing the speed to the to watch closely.
at first, i thought it might be an airplane but then i noticed that there was no fuselage, no wings, no engines, no track, so i concluded that an ordinary plane was not, then i thought it might be a weather balloon but i did not observe any material known and it was a ball of bright yellow light radiating in every direction and with a constant velicity in a concrete pattern and that afternoon there was no wind, reason why it concludes that it could only be an unidentified flying object.
the object was a ball of bright yellow light flying over faro's airspace at an altitude that allowed me to see it shifting south to north and past the infant's path next to faro's knot plus a few meters to the west flying over the hills, disappearing over them as they headed north.
i felt calm and observant of a rare phenomenon that i had never noticed and my reaction was of surprise and curiosity in relation to that unknown and unusual object.
as i was about to drive i always tried to visualize the ball of bright yellow light with the safety of the car but there was no automobile traffic nearby which allowed me to slow down and see the bright yellow ball disappear over the two hills heading north.
description: Ball of light radiating a yellow color in all directions following a set path with steady speed in the sky above faro heading northward passed over the infant track and two high hills when i stopped seeing it.

detailedDescription:
I was on night duty in my employers villa in lamanga, i  was doing a night check on living room, when i looked towards the east and saw this huge white pulsating light, i observed it a while, then looking at the size of the moon in relation to this object i realised how huge it must be. so i got my iphone 7 plus out and tried to focus on the object to photograph it. the images fpeak for themselves, i was very unsure what i was looking at? at first i thought it might be a planet in the sky or a metiorite ? when i looked at the photographs it was beautiful a pinkish centre with very distinct rings the outter edge seems solid but on closer indpection you can see like gasses . 
i dont know what it was but it was an awsome sight and my photographs are so clear.
description: Pulsating bright white light with circles and a pink centre

detailedDescription:
Llegamos al lugar llamado barriada zapata de malaga (costa del sol).
eramos yo, mi mujer y una amiga eran las 21 horas o las 22 horas aproximadamente,hacia calor ya que era en el mes de agosto y habria una 
temperatura de entre 28 y mas de 30 grados.
era una noche sin viento y un cielo muy claro y estrellado salvo por lo que teniamos a nuestra izq que lo contare mas adelante.
era unos dias antes de la feria de malaga que por aquel entonces empezaba el dia 11 de agosto del 2012 porlo que calculo que tenia que ser el dia 7, no lo recuerdo bien pero seguro que fue antes de la feria.
recuerdo y no podria olvidarlo esa noche tan buena no habia animalesya que no se oian ni los grillos solo el agua del rio guadalorce, ni siquiera una picada a nuestras cañas solo en medio de esa bonita noche se escuchaba el relinchar de un caballo que estaba atado a nuestra derecha y aquel animal solo queria estar junto a nosotros con lo cual no paraba de acercarse a nuestro lado y mi mujer lo espantaba para que nos dejara tranquilos.
ya que a mi me daban miedo los caballos.
a nuestra izquierda a la altura de la copa de un gran eucalipto que alli habia se encontraban tres luces muy grandes como el reflejo de algun planeta pero muy cerca de la tierra tanto que era de una gran magnitud.
eran de un color amarillo (color calido),cuya formacion era triangular con base paralela a nuestro horizonte.Alli estubieron perfectamente entre 1 hora inmoviles y 2.Cuando volvi a mirar esas extrañas luces cambiaron su formacion colocandose en linea vertical a nuestro horizonte, justo al ratillo el que estaba mas alto digamos el numero 3 empezo a moverse cada vez mas rapido y a subir en direccion a casiopea que justo se cruzo con un avion de pasajeros elde enmedio se iva alejando perdiendo magnitud y el 1 que era el que estaba cerca de el horizonte se fue hacia eloeste y desaparecieron.
conozco a un investigador vuestro llamado juan vidal nicolau.
mi nombre es ange luis un saludo.
description: Igual que un planeta o estrella de gran magnitud

detailedDescription:
I was smoking a cigarette on a 2nd floor window of my house. my head was outside the window, as i was triyng to avoid the smoke to get inside the house. suddenly at my left side i saw a very brilliant sphere with a pure-constant and deep white light (absolutely not blinking in any way) travelling at a very fast speed of around 300-400km/h in a rectilineal trajectory and producing no sound. the object disappeared behind some trees, located 300-400 m from where i was. the maximum altitud of the object was 150-200 m. the whole sighten took place in between 2-3 seconds, but i could straight and clearly see it for almost two seconds. inmediately after the object dissapeared a lot of dogs started to bark (a lot, since it was in a rural-urbanised area).

i wasnt afraid at all and never startled, it was all very natural. it took me some seconds after the disappearing of the object that i realised it was a ufo. i realised it was a ufo, because the speed of the object was very high, and no sound was made (no plane of any kind, nor a drone, even less an helicopter). it wasn't a comet or some spatial rubish, because of the altitud, the trajectory and the speed. it just didnt matched with any kind of known object to me, in that place, time, area and other dettails.
sorry for the ortographic faults.
description: It was moving with a rectilinial movement at a constant speed of around 300-400 km/h

detailedDescription:
Late april 2000, 23 miles northeast of morón afb (seville), spain. around 7:15 p.M. still broad daylight, i was driving home from my workplace, alone as usual. there were no cars then on that stretch of back road from marchena to écija (province of seville, spain). i had just entered a mile and a half long straight section of road when from my left side, from behind a hill, as if taking off from the ground in a movement along an arc of circle, a streak of light caught my eye, which almost instantly i recognized as a red sphere of light that was coming right towards my car. i jumped in my seat but somehow my scare turned into cold-blooded curiosity when the sphere immediately came to a sudden halt, perhaps not more than 60 yards away from me, as if it had been aware of me, and then changed direction, and continued moving ahead of me in a straight line parallel to the road and then it started blinking within fractions of a second. it was then, very much to my surprise, that another orb of light, same size, this one yellowish, was wiggling behind the first orb, hurrying along from the same direction the first one had appeared, till it started tailing the first sphere in a straight line, both following the contour of the fields, blinking at the same time and flying very low, all the while parallel to the road. they slightly increased their speed and disappeared behind a low hill. from the start i had time to check my speed, first i was driving at 87 mph, then i lowered my window because i wanted to be sure that what i was watching was real and it sure was. i reduced speed trying to listen to some noise coming from the orbs, and i couldn't hear anything apart from the wind rushing in. both lights were perfect spheres, they had the size of a ping pong ball at arm’s length, maybe a little smaller. before they disappeared, i flashed my high beams for some seconds at the same time they were blinking. somehow i wanted them to know by doing so  that i was there. the whole episode may have lasted for about 30 seconds, at the most. as soon as i could pull over, i phoned my wife to tell her what i had seen. i was excited and she was nine months pregnant, and got a little scared. she asked me to get home as soon as possible, which i did. from then on i am absolutely sure that something really really strange is out there.
i had seen strange lights moving in the night sky before. on one occasion in córdoba (spain) in august, 1987 around 1:00 a.M, it was really weird. i was with a friend, we were sitting on his doorstep, chatting while looking at the stars. suddenly, a white star like light, which was there like any other star, started moving slowly, i nudged him pointing to the star and said: can you see what i see? he said suuure. the light stopped and then suddenly flashed out of sight. seconds later, it flashed back into sight again a little bit to our left and started jumping up and down in a zigzag motion crossing a large stretch of sky, and then suddenly flashed out of sight again at an incredible speed this time leaving a long streak of light behind. we were amazed and unable to identify what we had just seen. it definitely was not anything we could think of.
flightPath: Hovering then path,Straight-line path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering

detailedDescription:
Last week i saw 2 very bright orbs above the serra de monchique, moving very slowly. i made a report also on mufon because it was very weird. 
yesterday there was a fire in serra de monchique and we could see it from our house. we took pictures from the fire and suddenly we saw this very strange line above in the sky. at the exact place were last week the orbs were. i don't know how long it was there because i was constanly zooming in with my camera on the fire and could not see anything else. 
the only simular i found on internet was in 2014 strange zigzag lines above hawai. 
it's in the rightcorner above, you can zoom in for a clear detail.

detailedDescription:
it was closed night, just after having dinner and talking all with each other in the roof of the building where there was a big terrace.

then a mate and me watch the ufo lightned just by the city lights, it did not glow or have any visible light but it reflected the lights of the city, it just appeared flying so low the city lights made us able to see it, its shape was strange because it was so "small" to have anyone inside it, now i think it could be a drone, it was a thin cylinder rememebered me the city tube street lights but bigger, long as a city bus maybe or a truck, and a lot of spheres from the start to the end of it symetricaly situated.

we could not hear anything apart from the city noises, it flied real low and close to us as it passed away we stop being able to see it as there were other buildings around. it flew in a perfect straight line and at slow maintained speed.

maybe someone has seen things like this. it was some years ago but i remembered very well the shape and the way it flyed so steady and silently.

best regards.
description: At night we were having dinner at building roof, then watched a cilinder with balls in between thing flying over.

detailedDescription:
I live in southern spain. 

last night, me and my family were chilling outside our cottage, when at around 23:45 (local time), we saw a group of approx. 10 white lights (just like stars), blinking, moving and grouping in the sky. they started to form shapes, first a big circle then a vertical line and then a strange symbol like a question mark.

they moved in groups of 3 and were constantly blinking. during this entire exhibition we could see how the lights got closer and further to us at a fast speed, then something similar to a bright red shooting star crossed the area leaving a red trail. finally, the lights started to fade until they disappeared, all this lasted for 30 minutes or so, we called our friends and were shaking all the time.

10 minutes after they disappeared, some aircrafts started to overfly the area, coming from different angles but all of them going to the same spot, one every couple of minutes, which is completely unusual. 

we are all pretty sceptics with these things but when this happened, we were shaking, it was the most incredible thing we ever saw and we can’t find an explanation. i’ve searched a lot but couldn’t find anything, i found some tweets from people that may have seen the same at the same time, but just a couple and that’s all…

we’ve read about satellite lights and it’s definitely not that. 

our first thought was that it could be some drone exhibition or tests but everything that happened around it was just too weird (the red shooting star, all the aircrafts flying the area after the lights disappeared…).

tried to record this and take some pictures we didn’t have any proper equipment and our phones wouldn’t show it.
description: Over 10 white lights in the sky, moving in groups of 3 forming shapes, getting closer and further

sorry cant be more helpful just want to get it off my chest.


sorry cannot give my personal details this would get me dismissed from my job, sorry.

detailedDescription: I was working and cleaning outside when i saw at first three bright balls just slowly floating,i wondered what they were,balloons,plastic bags maybe.I remember thinking fuengirola market is on so probably carrier bags caught in the wind.Then i saw another two or three  maybe four following.At that moment i thought hey they look just like the orbs i've seen on you tube.Thats when i decided to film them with my iphone however every time i am pointing the camera at them i couldn't see them on the screen.I could see them clearly looking over the phone but still not on screen but i carried on filming.I then stopped had  quick look on playback then started filming again.I just thought point it at them and follow them and then i'll check it later.When i checked i could briefly see a couple.Thats why i contacted you guys because maybe you can enhance or zoom or whatever to see what they were.I am pretty sure i was pointing straight at them.I just hope it won't be a waste of your time ie if they are balloons or something like that.I filmed them until they went over the house and out of view.

detailedDescription:
1) i was at a sister in law village for vacation.
2) a child scrim calling me, to see the sky.
3) a ufo
4) description of action. first, it came from south over our heads and stand write in front of us. as if it they study us, or, as they try to communicate something. i have my baby on my arms, and other three children we were five in total. it moves so slowly, and the light look like it breathe. after 5 minutes, it moves over horizon north direction for few meters, and then it despaired up over in the sky very very fast. 
5) feeling during the view: first i was astonish, then a feel strange, as they want me to tell something, i´m artist and poet, and years after, i feel as i have a message to earth, about ourselves. children and i we stay quiet, and when it left, i told them all to go inside the house, and i give them some pencils and pens, and i ask them to draw what each one have seen, and i put them in different rooms, so, they will not copy their drawings each other. then i match the draws, and i prove that all of us saw the same object. then i call by phone to newspaper, but the answer me that it should be a balloon. however, we all knew it wasn´t. the children, now, one is schizophrenic, the other get married and lives in other place, the other i don´t remember even her name, and my child who was in my arms, and that have 4 month of born when we witness, his is almost 39 year old. 
6) it despaired very fast like if it will be aspirated, absorbed by the cosmos, over our heads.

detailedDescription:
I was playing in a bar with my jazz band. at one point the audience started standing up and pointing at the sky. after a while we stopped playing and went to check it out. when i looked up i saw dozens of lights in a shape almost rectangular. i got shocked and felt some kind of fear of the unknown. my first reaction was to capture it on film, but my cellphone has low quality so it couldn't capture the small lights, then we tried the iphones, and they still didn't capture it. so we stood there and watched, there were about 30 people on the bar watching it. the formation from my prespective made a rectangule of 5-8 centimeters in the sky, it had a synchronized flux of energy that pulsated down->up. 
the formation started moving really slow and diagonally from sw to s and then moved up. it slightly changed of shape during its course but maitained a synchronized formation. then we were asked by the bar's owner to keep playing, so i didn't get to see it disappear. the next day when i went to check my facebook and a friend of my who is also a musician, was playing on another bar in the same town. he had posted " what are these shiny dots in the sky? ", then i realised we could have about 70 witnesses on this event, just in ferragudo. it was big enough to have been seen from nearby cities.

thanks, joão romão
description: A formation of lights acsenting, pulsating glow down to up. changed shape and unable to film

detailedDescription:
All of the class were taken to see the stars around 10:40pm, but about half of the class left 10 minutes later. i stayed with the monitor and some friends, they were pointing and explaining constellations, i was really bored so i sat down on the grass and looked the opposite way. it was then when i noticed a boomerang-like object with a tiny dome and four flashing lights: yellow, blue, white and red. at first, i thought it was a plane, but i had seen planes flying a from a long distance and they did not fly that worryingly fast. i noticed that it suddenly stopped a couple times in the middle of the air for no apparent reason, then it continued it's path. 

it disappeared into the trees, but i didn't see signs of it descending. it came back another 4 times around our area, abruptly stopping and rerouting as if it was looking for something in particular. it also started to fly in circles at one point. i tried to tell my friends, and they saw it too but they did not seem to pay much attention.

i have seen planes and jets flying at all sorts of distances and i repeat - this object was much faster than the usual. i tried to record and take pictures, but the sky was way too dark and the phone camera wouldn't catch what i saw. i know it sounds stupid and crazy without any evidence but it was not normal at all.
flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change,Other

description: Ufo sighting near the cathedral of sevilla (spain)

detailedDescription:
Sorry for any mistakes in the content, as english is not my first language.

this was my very first sighting of any kind. i had experienced some weird situations or events in the 

past but in terms of seeing anything unsual or weird outdoors, this is was the first time.

i saw an orb of brigh light in the air outdoors (but not in the sky or closer to it) at the end of san 

luis street in the city of faro, algarve, portugal. it was on a monday, 15th september of 2014 at 8:30 

pm from this coordinates (37.024195, -7.923251). i saw it flying around 10/11 meters in hight from the 

ground and it was like 20/30 meters away from me in distance. it just crossed the street i was walkin 

in, from the right to the left, in a perfect horinzontal straigh line trajetory or path (about like 5 

meters) at a very slow velocity (around 10km/h), like the velocity of a bike going slow. it was just 

seen for a few seconds, 3 to maybe 5 and of a sudden it was gone, not leaving any trail. i did't see it 

shrink, it just went out of my sight of sudden, just like when someone turn off the light in a room. 

you dont see it shrink or the light bulb going away, it just simply goes out of sight. that's what 

happen, just after when i saw just for a few seconds. the 'orb' was a circle of light perfectly round 

with about 5, 6 cm in diameter (without any kind of sparks around it), it had a brigh white light very 

intense, of just one color, and didn't leave any trail.

in faro city, it wasnt dark already. it was that dark blue just before it goes black so i could still 

see the buildings, houses and the sky perfectly. i was walking on the street on my way home (i dont do 

it very often, just from time to time, i go for a walk to some place and then return home) and usually 

i walk lookin down to see where i step in, and of a sudden something made me to look and raise my head, 

not to the front, but up because i realised that something bright was flying just a few meters away 

from me. it was an automatic and instinctive behavior. the street where it happens has houses (1st 

floor) of both sides and whatever that crossed that night it just passed over just a few meters in 

hight above the roofs/balconys of the houses. there was nobody else in street and there was no cars 

driving by either on that moment.

i confessed that i never whitness anything like it, but right in the moment we think that it is 

somthing caused by our eyes or our tired head. but truth is, i saw it and follow its movement for 

around seconds and of a suden it was gone. it wasnt any kind of flying entertainment instrument/toy 

that i would have known of. and i discard aswell any kind of soap bubble lightened by the streets 

lamps. by the informations of the distances and hights already mentioned, the chance of being any kind 

of plane, helicopter, satelite, chinese flahslight, led ballon, laser, meteorite or star is definetly 

out of question in my mind. there was no possibility of recording due to its brief appearance.

i can reveal that for my own experience that during the sighting and in a fraction of seconds, the mind 

tries incessantly for an answer for whatever the eye is seeing but after exclusion after exclusion (is 

not a ballon, not a bug, not a toy, not a lantern, not a laser, etc), when the phenomen just stops, the 

mind become even further and more perplexed than when it just faced with the problem. simply because, 

all plausible assumptions (that the mind got in its database) were simply set aside. the mind couldn't 

coincide or make sense, whatever it was, with absolutly anything that i have seen live or making part 

of our known and 'apparent' world or physical reality.

right after the sighting, i tried to memorize in my mind the 'visual image' of what i just whitnessed 

and being just 2 minutes away from home walkin, i was already thinkin what kind of device or phenomenon 

 could resemble such thing, in order to search on internet when i get home. just before thinkin of a 

paranormal possibility, i though first to certify if there was actually nowdays any kind of toy or 

'drone' ressembling what i saw. of course that my eyes, knew what they saw and perfectly knew that it 

was not toy but my rational mind wanted by all means to find an explanation for it. cause one thing is 

to see those whitish circles in pics (those typical called 'orb's of dust that show on photographs), 

another is to whitness with your own eyes a circle of light passing just through your eyes not too far 

away. i knew it would be probably very dificult of find something similar in video on internet, cause i 

had the true belief that that thing wasnt a device/toy.

although i was unable to capture it on video, to my big surprise when i arrived home, i simply digited 

on my pc 'bright orb' and on a video search, i could found exactly what i was lookin for, exactly what 

i saw. i couldnt believe my eyes. after all, that circle of light outdoors minutes ago, wasnt a product 

of my mind, it wasny my eyes playing tricks on me. if this thing is captured on video, therefore it 

wasnt an alucination i just had. whatever it was, it happened and i saw it. gezzz, iam not crazy. (i 

thought, ;)

its important to say that i never across or saw in my entire life these type of light orbs in any 

videos. for sure ive seen ufo docs through the years on tv but never came across to these type of light 

balls in any videos. ufos to me were synonymous of 'flying metal machines', those flying saucer crafts 

drive by those little aliens creatures so usually portrayed in such docs or movies. these type of 

'light orb' thing i never saw it on tv or any media, it it was the case, i would for sure would have it 

recognise in the first place in street. it was simpy the most weird thing ever i just saw in my entire 

life. it was just for a few seconds but it made me very interested to find out what on earth was that.

i'll leave though some links found on internet that shows in a very accurately way, what i just 

whitness in faro (city), but in faro it was seen with a much lower altitude than what its shown in the 

videos.

i confessed that when i first saw it, i really though it was something psychic or illusory (cause i 

just came from hospital that night from a visit and my mind could be, who knows, a bit tired). but 

could my eyes created all of that? fact is, that later as i mentioned, i searched for it on internet 

and i find and see the same 'orbs' in videos already taped by other people and realise that this is 

apparently a phenomenon that is already happening at a worldwide level for so many years already.

whether or not these videos are real, all i can say is that they're truly similar to what i saw, and as 

i mentioned, i didn't have any knowledge about the balls of light in video whatsoever, and specially in 

such particular and unsual way, just right in the middle of the street or sky. ive never experienced so 

far nothing of the genus, so iam still considering to which point this phenomenon is real or common 

either in portugal or in any other places of the world. and iam not talking about a tiny luminous dot 

flying above my head just like a plane or something similar.

a circle of light with 5/6cm in diameter (size of a tenis ball) just crossed and appeared in front of 

me at 10 meters hight (about the size of an apartment with 3,4 floors cause thats what mine has), just 

a few meters away from me in the middle of the street, without making any sound. it didnt look 

spherical, it didnt had an spherical format, it look like a plane circle, because it was only from one 

tone of light, without any shadows, therefor without any tridimensional appearance. but it was a tone 

of light so strong that i dont remember seeing anything like it, and as strange and weird as it seems, 

it was perfectly definite. i could only compare the intensity of light to the scoocer/football stadium 

lights, but if you try to look at them, we can barely look at, cause we get to see all the reflections 

and sparks shoting in all directions. it wasnt the case with the orb. though it was very very bright, i 

could stare at it for a millions years if it let me, it didnt hurt or blinded my eyes as a car's light 

would, though the light of the 'orb' was very very powerful.

personaly i dont have a big belief of the existence of extraterrestial lifes/beings similar to ours, in 

which some kind of other humanoids races come to visit us or to spy us but after what i jsut saw, i 

dont discard the possibility of the existence of another type of existences or energeitc 

entities/organisms to which we are not awake for or have knowledge.



these are some videos i found (not mine), note that the light color shown on the videos is nothing like 

in real life. the 'orb' is like 100x brighter than it shows on video:

1º italy - at minute '40:18' (the one flying behind the trees): -

2º - [link moved to fi section/cms/tg]

best regards

detailedDescription:
Vivo en sanlucar de bda.  en la avenida de la atalaya, un camino que lleva a un antiguo cortijo a la salida de sanlucar, entre las carretera  hacia trebujena y carretera de jerez.
el caso viene a ser que cuando salgo de mi trabajo, voy al gimnasio y suelo llegar tarde, pero este d''a llegue algo mas temprano, sobre las 21:40 o poco mas. al entrar en mi casa aun no hab''a llegado mi mujer y mi hijo y el perro, rufo, estaba inquieto, deseando salir. sin cambiarme de ropa, con las mayas de ciclo-in, cog'' la correa del perro y salimos de mi casa hacia el final del camino. siempre llevo al rufo amarrado por el camino por si pasa alguien, alguna moto o coche y cuando paso la ultima casa lo suelto. el perro en el momento de verse libre siempre tiende a correr como un loco por el campo, pero el este dia se quedo quieto a mi lado. para que corriese coji un palo que estaba junto a mi y lo lance al campo. algo se movi'', cre'' que seria un conejo y pens'' que el perro al verlo ir''a a por el. al mirar al perro segu''a junto a mi lado y le grite "vamos rufo". 
algo volvi'' a moverse y en esta ocasi''n segu'' el movimiento del forraje con la vista asta que al llegar a la altura del camino vi perfectamente la silueta de, lo mas parecido a un hombre, de color gris oscuro, que en una posici''n como de firmen militar, cruzaba el camino a unos 10 metros de mi, perdi''ndose  el movimiento entre unos invernaderos.
quise ver algo mas pero entonces, al final del camino, a la altura del cortijo de la atalaya vi como una luz como un faro potente que se acercaba por el camino y luego ascend''a perdiendo poco a poco su brillo y ganando velocidad.
pense que el ser que yo vi era imposible que uniese llegado asta la luz para macharse en ella y que pod''a estar aun por all''. el cortijo podr''a encontrarse a unos 800 metros desde donde yo estaba y mirando hacia el cortijo el ser paso de izquierda a derecha. 
me entro en este momento mucho miedo y me volv''. por cierto el perro ya me estaba esperando en la puerta de casa.

detailedDescription: I was recently flipping through some pictures i took of my trip to granada, nicaragua in 2011. in two pictures, i saw what appeared to be strange objects in the sky. although they appear small, if you zoom in with computer software such as windows photo viewer, you can see these objects take better shape. honestly, i am not able to answer a majority of the questions listed above because i didn't even notice these objects until now; in fact, the qualities i checked off above only related to the description i was able to get from the 2 photos. i know the date and approx. time of the trip because i checked my passport to see what day i was actually in nicaragua. also, i don't believe these objects to be anything on the lens because i took other pictures as well and all the others are clear without anything else in the sky with the exception of birds. the birds that appear in the other pictures are jet black. also, as you can see, the day was beautiful with a lot of sun and virtually no clouds. i am curious to get some insight as to what these objects may be. i don't buy that they are balloons or weather phenomenon but rather some sort of craft. also, the pictures were in no way edited and these images were in no way manipulated from the original image. i used a regular sony point and shoot camera with i believe 10-12 megapixel capability.
description: 2 pictures found from my trip to nicaragua with objects in them.

detailedDescription:

detailedDescription:
I was driving home on a semi busy road here in the algarve portugal, which is surrounded by mountains. the mountains are not large like the ones in british columbia but large none the less. i saw a very bright light which the only other thing that high up could have been is the front end of an airplane with the front headlight pointed exactly towards where i was driving behind other cars heading home. there is an airport not to far away in the city of faro, which is where i was leaving. being here a while now i can generally tell the flight patterns and with this wide open sky i can differ from certain types of planes and helicopters.. anyway.. this particular light i saw was near dusk and lower than any normal star and brighter than normal. i was mentioning the mountains before because that is what i am using as a reference. the light was not much higher than the mountain and i kept my yes on the road but constantly looking at the light which i noticed it move a bit back and forth. it was basically almost straight ahead of me at this point about 5 miles ahead or so when suddenly it veered at a super speed and still lit about a mile south or so then instantly took off upwards and it was gone. the catch is that i've now seen it 3 night in a row. today i got off work at 3pm and did some errands reached home here about 6. i saw it again tonight and when i came inside to grab something the light which i've seen now for the last few night was basically in the same sort of area and when i came back outside it was gone. i know it was what i saw the last few nights because of the location. this week i am going to purchase a good night vision video camera because with this big open sky that i have above me i would like to get some get some great video of this. 
 if you have any questions please feel to call my cell phone or email me. with the phone numbers that i left you do not include area codes, just the straight numbers. thanks.
description: Glowing very very brightly. very rapid movement abruptly south then an immediate take off upwards out of sight.

detailedDescription: I was at an outoor social event when someone pointed out a strange flying object approaching from the distance. witnesses agreed that it looked like a giant golly doll. it appeared to be black with some red on the lower parts. after it had passed about half a mile away from us it became apparent that it was tall and thin in profile. at least 8 people saw it and nobody in the group offered any plausible explanation as to what it was and none noticed any sound from it. after it had passed its side profile became apparent - it was like a vertical rectangle. it continued on straight-line course apparently at a steady altitude of perhaps 500-1000ft before it went out of sight beyond buildings in the distance. a lot of more people must have seen it. if i only seen the front view of it i would have thought it was a strange-looking helicopter or balloon but the lack rotors and this side profile with no tail and the lack of audible sound somewhat negates the helicopter theory and as for it being balloon and thin side profile makes me think doubtful about that. somebody must know what it was.
description: This airborne golly-shaped object was seen by at least 8 people.

detailedDescription:
From the roof of a house in the historical center of seville, some friends and i have seen and ufo while we were looking at the moon eclipse. 

one of my friends realised that a big and shiny yellow-orange light was coming from the opposite orientation of the moon. especifically it was going straight with constant height from the north-west to south east (in that moment the direction was going almost the situation of the covered moon).

right after watch it we realise that it was not a plane (one of my friends in the roof is aeronautical engeneer and he corroborated that it wasn't a normal flying object).

the intensity of the light, the color, the speed and the height were all constant. it was going faster than a plane considering the apparent height.

when we saw it we were excited because of what we were seeing, but we did not feel anything strange. it wasn't doing any strange noise as we could heard.

after 2 minutes watching it and going further, the perspective that we had in the roof of our building didn't allow us to see it anymore.

i'm attaching one video that i could record, i didnt have enough time to record it when it was closer, so the only thing that you'll see in the video is an small orange light.
description: Bright sphere shape object, orange color, constant speed, straight movement

detailedDescription: The print was found and a scan made 12/5/09. my father never mentioned seeing the object but when we returned to the states in 1959, i remember him being a friend of roger early who was somehow connected with project blue book. i believe the neg may have been given to early. i do know that from living in torremolinos, kids back then did not play with kites, model planes or paper planes. all the kids on the beach were poor fishermen's kids. my father used a nikon rangefinder camera, plus-x film and was shooting the fishing boat to use as a subject in one of his paintings. he was a famous painter (google: ben stahl). the exposure seems to be f8 or 16 @ 1/250 or 1/125 because of the frozen action of the waves in the photograph and the depth of field. it's not a blur of a bird, tear on the neg or delamination on the print. the print has a fold (visable on the picture across the horrizon). the surface of the original print is clean. i used "unsharp mask" in photoshop to bring the scan in better focus. this produced marking on the body of the object. note the shadows on the object are consistant with shadows on the man behind the boat. the man is shielding his eyes and looking at something down the beach, in the sky or out at sea and not at the object overhead. perhaps there were two objects? the object in the photogeaph has an odd perspective as it looks far away yet close over the shore line. also, note the disturbance in the air at both ends of the object. it also cannot be something on the lens as this would be totally blown out of focus. i've searched other photographs and have failed to see any other object with the same shape. bruce maccabee saw the image and could not come up with an answer as to what it could be. nothing in a camera, especially a slr, can produce such an effect. if something was thrown in front of the camera it would not have produced the "air disturbance" as shown - these are not developing streaks either. please let me know what you think. regards, david stahl
description: Photographed by my father 1958. print found recently

detailedDescription:
Nací en 1979 en junio, desde que tenía 4 años de edad hasta mis 12 años aproximadamente he tenido pesadillas que eran recurrentes donde me lavnataba a media noche lllrnsdo desesperado y aterrado y mis padres tardaban horas en hacer que recuperará la calma, en mis pesadillas los actores cambiaban su forma según cada pesadilla, unas veces se les veía otras veces no, a veces con forma de robots, otras de monstruos. siempre me veía en una habitación sumamente oscura y frente a mí una gran pantalla luminosa como las pantallas led que hoy son comunes pero que en aquella época eran solo ficción, en esa pantalla aparecían varias secuencias de números que yo debía seguir o completar con mi mano sobre aquella pantalla presionando números aleatorios, esas entidades me obligaban a hacer esa secuencia solo que nunca hablaban pero yo sabía lo quqe querían, luego esa secuencia se hacía más y más rápida y cuando no podía seguir la secuencia ellos presionaban en mi mente para seguir haciéndolo y era cuando despertaba llorando y aterrorizado

estás pesadillas pasaban más o menos cada mes o a veces duraban tres o cuatro meses sin suceder y dejaron de pasar más o menos desde que cumplí 12 años,lo curioso es un niño de 4 años o hasta 6 y 7 con pesadillas de números que eran parecidos a lo que se conoce como la secuencia fibonacci que cuando la descubríamos después  la asocie de inm disto con mis pesadillas.

otro dato curioso es que cuando tenía 24 años sufrí unas convulsiones por un problema familiar que me llevó a esa situación y el hecho que me desmayara me llevaron a hacer unos estudios médicos entre ellos un electro encefalograma y radiografías de mi cerebro y el doctor juan josé sánchez encontró justo en el centro de mi cerebro un extraño cuerpo del tamaño de un grano de arroz que era anómalo y extraño lo que el describió como un tumor, me pidió que justo un año después volviera hacer los estudios para ver si cambiaba de tamaño y al hacerlo no había cambiado su tamaño original por lo que el doctor dijo que no me preocupara por el

siempre he tenido la curiosidad por el tema ovni, una vez a mis trece años junto a mi mamá y una amiga de la casa vimos a lo lejos a las 5:30 ok un ovni en forma de cigarro que subía lentamente en el cielo a lo lejos y luego como si hubiese volteado o girado de vertical a horizontal se convirtió en un punto que desapareció, siempre he investigado el tema ufo ovni, y a veces siento que no encajo en la sociedad, tengo algunas premoniciones que se cumplen y con mi esposa actualmente hemos tenido experiencias extrasensoriales en unas tres ocasiones en 5 años de casados,en las que cosas que pienso ella las ha recibido.

quisiera saber si esa experiencia q la cual nadie nunca me ha dado respuesta tenga algo que ver con el fenómeno ovni y sea producto de algún tipo de abducción ... muchas gracias amigos de mugon. espero pueda ayudarlos a en su busuqueda de la verdad...

detailedDescription:
I was two to four years old and a friend approached me and others during the morning break at kindergarten (i can recall some of the names but the contact is lost). our friend pointed us to the sky where a coppery oval was stationary very close to the sun. the object was at a distance from the sun that not permitted continuous surveillance but enough to allow a definite observation of the object. the object reflected the sunlight as a metallic object would in its position. the surface and thence the reflection was very shiny (see the report form for the rest of the description). 
we discussed if it was a plane as we kids, were told about and had seen planes and helicopters. these were the only objects i knew that could fly. 
i do not recall exactly the conversation and my fellows points on it but finally someone proposed to report the event to our teacher because we couldn't reach any conclusion. we all agreed. in the meanwhile we were checking the object in order to ensure what we saw and to try to get some clue of what it was. i personally discarded it was a plane because it was stationary it was different from the planes we had seen in other occasions from the yard. from our point of view the planes moved very slowly while this object wasn't. moreover, the object seemed to be closer and bigger at sight than planes.
firstly i felt confused because i was noticing something i wasn't told about before. then i felt willing to know what it was. i also acknowledged i would ask my parents about it. i also felt confident because the majority of us agreed it was different from any known flying object we were told about. 
this conversation took some minutes, from three to eight logiacally and as i recall. subsequently we went for the teacher. unfortunately during our seek nobody was checking if the object was still there and when we finally reported the event we all realized that it was gone.
description: Stationary coppery oval next to the sun. witnessed by half a dozen scholars.

detailedDescription:
I observed a sphere in the water for over one minute whilst on a voyage between valencia and palma de mallorca. this was a near one track passage on 39degrees 25 mins between the two points. the vessel was a sailing yacht but there was no breeze so we were motoring. 

we had lost the engine and generator for around an hour prior to the sighting and had been floating whilst fixing this issue (fuel related). the mediterranean sea is non-tidal and with no breeze we moved very little over the period. other vessels were several miles away and we were not in any danger. 

i had already noted the depth at around 1400m - nearly the deepest part of the sea at this point between the mainland and island - known as the iberian trench - extending to around 1500m depth.

once we were underway again i was on watch, with one other person below. due to the uncommonly calm water - often called millpond - very calm with little wave motion, we had been spotting sea life - a whale, several turtles, dolphins, and various garbage - there's not much more to do on a passage such as this.

for context i am an experienced sailor and had been engaged to deliver a swan 82 sailboat. i have several sailing qualifications, sailed in many oceans throughout my life and am very familiar with the sea - what's in it, how things move through it, etc. i have lived in the med for nearly twenty years, sailing and swimming often.  the yacht has a light grey hull and long >4m keel. outside of the calm waters the only other uncommon aspect had been the circa one hour stationary - over such deep water and in such a position this isn't a normal place to just float.

i was on the port helm looking forward past the mast and my eyes picked up an object in the water just ahead of the mast - we were traveling due east and the object appeared to be stationary - we were motoring at around 8 knots so anything floating would travel past at a reasonable speed but one which made it easy to notice and track objects to identify them - and with my knowledge of marine life this is usually an easy task.

the object i tracked with spherical, bright white but appeared pearlescent in the water. it was around the size of a baseball, at a depth of .5m - 1m and stationary as we went past it. the mast was about thirty feet in front of me so i had time to notice and focus on the object.  

my initial thought was that it was a jellyfish but i dismissed this quickly, then a manmade object - mooring ball or plastic ball of some type.  i was staring at this as it travelled down the length of the port side of the boat for several seconds whilst i tried to identify it. 

as it got closer to my position on the stern i sensed i was being observed, an odd feeling with made me consider whether it was the eye of a shark, whale, dolphin, other creature. the sun was near overhead and bright, visibility was perhaps >30m - the depth makes it difficult to judge how far down but with the clear pond like water and sun overhead anything would have been outlined.  

as the object approached being parallel with me it started to move and keep pace with the boat.  this alerted me to this being 'alive' - it would be unusual for a creature to float past a motoring boat at this close distance without retreating, for it to begin to swim in the same direction and at the same speed was most odd.  i then started for perhaps 45 seconds at the object - it didn't change depth, there was no observable wash or anything which might indicate motion through the water. i concluded it was not a part of any creature, it was just a sphere, now tracking the boat and i felt it was looking at me as much as i was looking at it. 

i considered whether it was a lobster/crab pot with a line caught around our keel but the sea is too deep, the sphere too small and there was no lines attached to it, our speed was constant.

as i observed this sphere it began to move through the water in random but straight parallel tracks of 0.5m - 1m.  it would be consistent with something approach the speed of a scared fish, but the way it altered direction felt precise and it was still tracking the boat in the same direction.  

at this point i became baffled and turned to call the other crew member below to come up and see this object.  as i turned back i caught sight of it now falling back from my position in the helm and around another 5.10 feet back it vanished. there was no wash, no other visible signs to account for what must have been a very rapid acceleration and it was no longer visible.

i cannot account for this and have considered it and discussed it with sailing friends since. the other crew member joked that it must have been a ufo (floating object) and remarked that he'd been tracked for two days by a white spherical flying object on a voyage from greece the previous summer, something he could not account for but all of the crew observed this.

i recently watched the tic-tac video and the reported movement of this object above the water correlates with what i observed, on a smaller scale and distance.  hence i decided to report this to enquire as to whether there have been any other such sightings.

the below link is an approximate location of the sighting on a sea chart.
http://map.Openseamap.Org/?Zoom=9&lat=39.52935&lon=1.36084&mlat=39.54736&mlon=1.41577&mtext=approximate%20location%20of%20sighting&layers=bftfftffftf0fffffffftt

i would like to reiterate that i am an experienced sailor and user of the sea, living on mallorca for nearly 20 years and used to swimming with sea creatures and identify them. i am accustomed to the way objects float and move through the water and no alcohol had been consumed alcohol ahead of nor on the voyage. 

this object struck me as sentient and fabricated, not naturally occurring or inanimate. 

jms
